www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/dozens-of-female-idf-spotter-recruits-refuse-to-serve-in-unit-after-assignment/0000018d-3c26-d07d-a79d-fde7dbf60000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯火箭弹杀死 21 名以色列士兵：加沙制造的串联弹头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/rpg-that-killed-21-israeli-soldiers-was-homemade-by-hamas/0000018d-3bca-d35c-a39f-bbda880e0000</link><description>导致建筑物倒塌的RPG发射器70年前首次开发，是一种轻型便携式反坦克武器</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 16:45:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/rpg-that-killed-21-israeli-soldiers-was-homemade-by-hamas/0000018d-3bca-d35c-a39f-bbda880e0000</guid></item><item><title>女子因涉嫌袭击以色列部长而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/rehovot-resident-arrested-on-suspicion-of-attacking-lawmaker/0000018d-3bdd-d07d-a79d-fbff7cd60000</link><description>环境保护部长伊迪特西尔曼对一名 52 岁妇女提出投诉，指控她掌掴和威胁</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 16:32:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/rehovot-resident-arrested-on-suspicion-of-attacking-lawmaker/0000018d-3bdd-d07d-a79d-fbff7cd60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队考虑用反坦克导弹武装约旦河西岸定居点的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-weighs-plan-to-arm-west-bank-settlements-with-anti-tank-missiles/0000018d-3b7e-d32b-adcf-ff7e83330000</link><description>此举是应右翼政客和约旦河西岸定居点居民的要求，旨在武装平民安全小组，以抵御 10 月 7 日发生的袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 15:47:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-weighs-plan-to-arm-west-bank-settlements-with-anti-tank-missiles/0000018d-3b7e-d32b-adcf-ff7e83330000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦偷车贼更喜欢电动车型：“你可以照亮房子几天”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/palestinian-car-thieves-prefer-electric-models-you-can-light-up-a-house-for-a-few-days/0000018d-3b00-d35c-a39f-bb5a3ac90000</link><description>去年汽车盗窃行业大约翻了一番，引发了 5.65 亿美元的保险索赔。在约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦地区，偷来的电动汽车电池甚至被用作发电机</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 14:18:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/palestinian-car-thieves-prefer-electric-models-you-can-light-up-a-house-for-a-few-days/0000018d-3b00-d35c-a39f-bb5a3ac90000</guid></item><item><title>在有关人质交易的报道中，以色列消息人士称，与哈马斯存在重大分歧，谈判可能会拖延</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/israeli-sources-differences-with-hamas-on-hostage-deal-significant-talks-may-last-long/0000018d-3b53-d3a5-afdf-7f77277d0000</link><description>报道显示，以色列和哈马斯广泛同意在为期一个月的停火期间进行人质囚犯交换。然而，哈马斯拒绝在没有承诺永久停止的情况下谈论细节，并将人质视为维持加沙平静和保护领导人生命的最重要杠杆。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:51:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/israeli-sources-differences-with-hamas-on-hostage-deal-significant-talks-may-last-long/0000018d-3b53-d3a5-afdf-7f77277d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的利库德集团部长和极右翼议员将出席以色列“加沙重新安置”会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/netanyahus-likud-ministers-far-right-mks-to-attend-gaza-resettlment-confab/0000018d-3b1e-d35c-a39f-bb5e38070000</link><description>几名以色列议员将于下周日参加在耶路撒冷举行的“胜利会议”，他们声称占领和重新安置加沙地带前以色列定居点是“唯一能带来安全的事情”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:41:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/netanyahus-likud-ministers-far-right-mks-to-attend-gaza-resettlment-confab/0000018d-3b1e-d35c-a39f-bb5e38070000</guid></item><item><title>现在不要向以色列人询问加沙巴勒斯坦人的伤亡情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/dont-ask-israelis-right-now-about-palestinian-casualties-in-gaza/0000018d-3770-d32b-adcf-f77227570000</link><description>最近对以色列人和巴勒斯坦人的民意调查得出了惨淡、令人痛苦的结果 — — 这就是为什么领导人，而不是他们破碎的人民，需要提供摆脱这场灾难的出路。但内塔尼亚胡提供的不是领导力，而是黑暗、冰冷的空虚</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:21:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/dont-ask-israelis-right-now-about-palestinian-casualties-in-gaza/0000018d-3770-d32b-adcf-f77227570000</guid></item><item><title>罕见地点：犹太以色列建筑工人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-rare-site-jewish-israeli-construction-workers/0000018d-3b2f-d3a5-afdf-7f3fef790000</link><description>随着以色列建筑业努力取代巴勒斯坦和外国工人，特拉维夫的一个工地找到了雇用最近退役士兵的解决方案</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:14:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-rare-site-jewish-israeli-construction-workers/0000018d-3b2f-d3a5-afdf-7f3fef790000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院命令耶路撒冷在安息日保持公共泳池开放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-court-orders-jerusalem-to-keep-public-pool-open-on-shabbat/0000018d-3b1e-d3a5-afdf-7f3f07570000</link><description>该裁决命令当地社区管理部门遵守耶路撒冷的现状，即宗教与世俗混合社区的公共泳池每周运营 7 天。一位副市长表示，耶路撒冷自由派屈服于宗教胁迫的日子已经结束了</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:13:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-court-orders-jerusalem-to-keep-public-pool-open-on-shabbat/0000018d-3b1e-d3a5-afdf-7f3f07570000</guid></item><item><title>学生抗议批评以色列军队的教师复职，阻止他重返教学岗位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/students-demonstrations-against-teacher-who-criticized-idf-prevent-his-return-to-teaching/0000018d-3aa0-d3a5-afdf-7fb799bb0000</link><description>市政府声称，学生对梅厄·巴鲁钦 (Meir Baruchin) 的抗议扰乱了高中的日常事务，法庭裁决推翻了梅厄·巴鲁钦 (Meir Baruchin) 的开除决定。校长在声明中写道，她无法“保证老师的安全”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 11:43:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/students-demonstrations-