hostage-deal/0000018d-371f-d32b-adcf-f77fb7860000</link><description>加沙与哈马斯的战斗开始类似于第二次黎巴嫩战争和第一次黎巴嫩战争期间的安全区 ■ 在没有取得明确和决定性胜利的情况下，以色列选择将重点放在敌人的伤亡人数上</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 17:59:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/heavy-casualties-in-gaza-spark-israeli-public-discourse-on-cease-fire-hostage-deal/0000018d-371f-d32b-adcf-f77fb7860000</guid></item></channel></rss>